data.description: Charming 3BR + Loft, 2.1BA corner townhome in sought after Briella, Boynton Beach. Tile throughout first floor and carpet upstairs. Freshly painted throughout. Master bedroom and bath on first level with dual sinks, roman tub and separate shower. 2BR + loft on second level. Briella is an all-ages, pet friendly community that offers residents resort-style amenities featuring heated swimming pool, brand new gym, playground, tennis and basketball. HOA covers roof, common grounds, ADT security & amenities.
